race.comment: Open race to close out the card. CHIEF WITNESS (9) loves this course and distance with a win and a placing from two attempts and is drawn to get the run of the race from gate two. Suitably placed here and expecting a very strong showing. SER JOH (3) was a touch disappointing last time out but go on the solid Doomben win two back. Capable of bouncing right back. ATMOSPHERE (1) saves his best form for this seven-furlong journey and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Top-three candidate on best figures. SCUD (2) wasn't disgraced at Listed level at the latest outing and should find this assignment much more to her liking. Don't dismiss lightly. SILVANITO (10) next best from the Doyle yard.
